{
  "text": "The computational environment used to perform the calculations is Mathematica 7.0, suitable due to its symbolic and high-precision numerical capabilities, as well as its large library of built-in routines that include packages for the computation of spheroidal harmonics [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
